fullText: 28th National A. M. S. A'sn's Con _Church of Our Father _ Cer of Lo & 12th streets Washington D.C. Headquarters - Hotel Arno
summaryText: Susan B. Anthony attended the 28th National A. M. S. A'sn's Con in Washington D.C. at the Church of Our Father on the corner of Lo & 12th streets. The headquarters were at the Hotel Arno.
